22:57.898 --> 23:01.597
Fuck!

23:01.597 --> 23:03.120
Fuck! Fuck!

23:05.906 --> 23:10.040
Someone get Tycho!

23:10.040 --> 23:11.128
Tiberius?

23:11.128 --> 23:13.043
You are fucking kidding me!

23:13.043 --> 23:14.871
- This is a joke.
- Shh. Keep your voice down.

23:14.871 --> 23:16.307
It could be worse.

23:16.307 --> 23:18.701
- Oh?
