24:13.364 --> 24:15.323
You forged his will?

24:15.323 --> 24:19.327
We can't have another civil war.

24:19.327 --> 24:21.982
Exactly. And what
was the alternative?

24:21.982 --> 24:24.332
We move now.

24:26.290 --> 24:28.858
I command the Army of the Rhine.

24:28.858 --> 24:31.165
Instead of leading it
into Germany,

24:31.165 --> 24:33.472
I lead it into Rome.

24:33.472 --> 24:35.822
Agrippa's gone,

24:35.822 --> 24:37.040
and Stepfather's
all over the place.

24:37.040 --> 24:38.477
This is the moment.

24:38.477 --> 24:40.479
He'll fight. You know he will.

24:40.479 --> 24:44.178
Not if he's dead,
like Marcellus.

24:44.178 --> 24:46.485
You get the poison.
I'll get the army.

24:48.748 --> 24:50.663
We'll have the Republic back
by the end of the year.

24:50.663 --> 24:53.970
Fuck.

24:53.970 --> 24:58.235
Livia...

24:58.235 --> 25:02.718
Unless, of course,
you're not really serious

25:02.718 --> 25:04.894
about ending his tyranny

25:04.894 --> 25:09.725
or avenging your father?

25:11.945 --> 25:13.773
Answer the question, Livia.

25:17.211 --> 25:20.736
