understand that.

25:30.703 --> 25:33.270
- It's too risky!
- So is waiting!

25:33.270 --> 25:34.489
- Shh.
- Tiberius is gone.

25:34.489 --> 25:35.925
What do you mean, "gone"?

25:35.925 --> 25:38.014
He left Rome with Vipsania
on horseback before dawn.

25:39.973 --> 25:41.235
They left the baby and this.

25:41.235 --> 25:44.673
It's for you.

25:47.937 --> 25:52.028
He's not coming back.
That's what it says.

25:52.028 --> 25:54.422
Find them. Get them back.

25:54.422 --> 25:58.078
Drusus. Drusus, please.

25:58.078 --> 26:00.254
No one else can do this.

26:00.254 --> 26:03.257
Find your brother.

26:03.257 --> 26:05.389
- Gaius will never forgive--
- To be continued.

26:16.792 --> 26:19.055
Antonina.

26:19.055 --> 26:23.277
Livia. Sorry, we're still
packing for Germany.

26:23.277 --> 26:25.584
Germanicus!

26:25.584 --> 26:28.761
