obviously been delayed.

26:28.761 --> 26:31.067
So you heard?

26:31.067 --> 26:34.288
Vipsania left me
Drusillus and a note.

26:34.288 --> 26:36.682
Couldn't believe it.

26:36.682 --> 26:39.989
What the fuck does Tiberius
think he's doing?

26:39.989 --> 26:41.730
