you want them to do.

26:57.659 --> 27:00.662
Drusus talks in his sleep.

27:00.662 --> 27:06.146
Things he wouldn't dare say
when he's awake.

27:06.146 --> 27:10.890
At first it didn't make
much sense. Just words...

27:10.890 --> 27:13.370
Fears.

27:13.370 --> 27:16.330
But in the end,
I got it.

27:16.330 --> 27:19.681
Of course
I've never told anyone.

27:19.681 --> 27:23.032
Not even Drusus.

27:23.032 --> 27:27.123
You see, that would be fatal.

27:27.123 --> 27:30.039
Yes, it would.

27:30.039 --> 27:32.520
People sometimes forget,

27:32.520 --> 27:34.827
my uncle killed my father,

27:34.827 --> 27:37.699
indirectly.

27:37.699 --> 27:40.920
Just like he killed yours.

27:43.749 --> 27:48.057
So, we're going
to restore the Republic.

27:48.057 --> 27:53.062
