28:24.877 --> 28:29.838
Yes. That's what I mean.

28:29.838 --> 28:31.666
Got it.

28:35.278 --> 28:37.977
Come on! Come on!

28:37.977 --> 28:39.935
Come on.

28:39.935 --> 28:43.678
You, come in.

28:43.678 --> 28:45.201
Come in.

28:45.201 --> 28:47.029
See? Look.

28:47.029 --> 28:48.248
Come on.

28:48.248 --> 28:50.076
Come in.

28:50.076 --> 28:54.036
All the pleasures of the world.

28:54.036 --> 28:56.691
See?

29:00.303 --> 29:03.263
Welcome, welcome.

29:03.263 --> 29:07.920
Wine for the lady.
Olives and grapes.

29:07.920 --> 29:10.879
Would the lady prefer
to see a man or a woman?

29:13.186 --> 29:16.189
Oh, I don't care, really.

29:21.498 --> 29:25.720
I'm the daughter of Augustus.

29:25.720 --> 29:28.375
And I've never had cunnilingus.

29:33.946 --> 29:36.644
Hello, gods.

29:36.644 --> 29:38.341
Hello, goddesses.

29:38.341 --> 29:41.475
It's me Vipsania Agrippina.

29:41.475 --> 29:42.650
Give me health.

29:42.650 --> 29:44.913
Give me sandals.

29:44.913 --> 29:47.786
And let me escape from Mother.

29:47.786 --> 29:50.919
And in return,

29:50.919 --> 29:53.487
I won't tell anyone
you don't exist.

29:59.362 --> 30:00.755
What is it?

30:00.755 --> 30:03.062
My happy childhood.

30:12.549 --> 30:15.596
Drusus gave this to me
on my eighth birthday.

30:15.596 --> 30:18.729
He stole it from Tycho.

30:30.524 --> 30:32.700
Where's its head?

30:39.620 --> 30:42.536
<i>Give me
that fucking horse!</i>

30:51.719 --> 30:53.112
What?

30:56.202 --> 30:57.856
My father broke off the head.

31:01.033 --> 31:02.121
Why?

31:05.254 --> 31:06.995
I don't know.

31:06.995 --> 31:08.736
<i>It's wine, Tiberius.
Try this.</i>

31:08.736 --> 31:11.870
Mmm. Here.

31:11.870 --> 31:14.176
Lad, have you
ever seen a clitoris?

31:14.176 --> 31:15.786
Yeah, come here.
Come here and show him.

31:15.786 --> 31:17.658
Sh... Show him your vulva.

31:17.658 --> 31:20.226
<i>For fuck's sake, Nero!</i>

31:20.226 --> 31:22.445
He's only a boy. Ow!

31:22.445 --> 31:24.099
<i>Get off!</i>

31:24.099 --> 31:26.275
You never talk about him.

31:26.275 --> 31:28.887
- Ever.
- Father.

31:32.412 --> 31:34.327
