31:35.981 --> 31:38.897
I said, is this Mother's?

32:09.797 --> 32:11.712
Put it on.

32:29.904 --> 32:33.168
It's funny, really,
if you think about it.

32:33.168 --> 32:34.822
Underneath it all,

32:34.822 --> 32:37.520
or even not
underneath any of it,

32:37.520 --> 32:39.958
