so taboo anyway?

32:51.186 --> 32:53.275
I'll tell you why,
'cause it's fucking awesome.

32:54.885 --> 32:58.150
Oh, come in,
we're open for business.

32:59.673 --> 33:01.283
Julia.

33:01.283 --> 33:03.894
Gracchus.

33:03.894 --> 33:07.115
Hello. How are you?
