How about you?

33:16.603 --> 33:18.474
Well, come on then, Gracchus.

33:18.474 --> 33:19.823
Fuck me.

33:22.565 --> 33:24.002
Everyone else has.

33:37.928 --> 33:39.408
Domitius.

33:40.844 --> 33:42.281
Are you waiting for me?

33:46.285 --> 33:48.504
Well, I was just
going to give thanks

33:48.504 --> 33:51.594
