34:11.049 --> 34:12.615
Do you remember Julia's lover

34:12.615 --> 34:14.443
that everyone was looking for
but never found?

34:14.443 --> 34:16.750
I'm the last fucking person
to forget about that.

34:16.750 --> 34:19.057
Do you think that it was Livia
that had Vilbia set up?

34:19.057 --> 34:21.668
Got Agrippa to kill him?

34:24.149 --> 34:25.715
Well, it certainly
wasn't Iullus.

34:25.715 --> 34:27.935
He can barely
wipe his ass with a sponge.

34:27.935 --> 34:30.024
Marcella.

34:36.813 --> 34:40.730
All right.
Here's what I do know.

34:40.730 --> 34:42.645
It was Livia who got
my mother to back off

34:42.645 --> 34:44.169
on Antonina's wedding,

34:44.169 --> 34:47.302
and I also know it was Livia
who uncovered the famine,

34:47.302 --> 34:49.652
back when...

34:49.652 --> 34:52.220
