if it's true or not?

35:21.162 --> 35:23.947
As long as
certain people think it is.

35:23.947 --> 35:26.124
That would be
an extremely dangerous game.

35:30.389 --> 35:34.654
If you want any kind of power
in this city,

35:34.654 --> 35:39.224
