are completely out of control.

38:09.548 --> 38:13.508
The situation's unstable.

38:21.734 --> 38:24.606
<i>Tiberius, wake up.</i>

38:24.606 --> 38:25.955
Wake up.

38:28.131 --> 38:31.091
