39:11.914 --> 39:13.568
She's a monster. Wake up!

39:20.575 --> 39:22.185
Oh, it's just a dream.

39:22.185 --> 39:26.320
It wasn't a dream.

39:26.320 --> 39:28.583
Ah, I couldn't breathe.

39:28.583 --> 39:32.848
Can you
put some clothes on?

39:32.848 --> 39:34.894
Leave us.

39:46.514 --> 39:48.864
I knew you wouldn't fuck off
to Greece without this rubbish.

39:54.000 --> 39:56.132
These are Mother's.

39:56.132 --> 39:58.134
