for months.

40:16.283 --> 40:19.460
What do you remember
about Father?

40:19.460 --> 40:22.420
Father?

40:22.420 --> 40:23.464
Nothing.

40:23.464 --> 40:25.205
Nothing at all?

40:32.604 --> 40:34.910
