41:43.979 --> 41:45.198
for anyone.

41:45.198 --> 41:47.374
It's not safe for <i>you.</i>

41:47.374 --> 41:49.289
I don't care about me.

41:49.289 --> 41:51.117
I know.

41:51.117 --> 41:57.384
I...

41:57.384 --> 41:59.386
I can't control it.

41:59.386 --> 42:05.827
Myself.

42:05.827 --> 42:07.568
Him.

42:10.876 --> 42:14.227
I can't do this without you.

42:14.227 --> 42:20.929
Oh, I...
I can't breathe.

42:20.929 --> 42:23.323
