you can't leave me alone.

42:27.719 --> 42:30.765
Tiber, no, no.

42:30.765 --> 42:33.202
No, stop. Stop.

42:33.202 --> 42:35.596
Stop. Stop it.

42:35.596 --> 42:37.250
No. Stop. Stop.

42:37.250 --> 42:40.122
- I'm a monster.
- No. No.

42:40.122 --> 42:41.559
You're not.
You're my brother.

42:41.559 --> 42:43.778
You're my--
you're my brother.

42:50.742 --> 42:51.699
Okay?

43:06.540 --> 43:10.457
Stupid self-confidence.

43:10.457 --> 43:12.590
Mother.

43:12.590 --> 43:15.897
Welcome back.

43:15.897 --> 43:18.552
- Are you fine?
- Yeah.

43:28.344 --> 43:30.303
It wasn't my idea,

43:30.303 --> 43:32.479
