would be pleased.

44:58.565 --> 45:01.524
Congratulations, Tiberius.

45:02.787 --> 45:04.702
I'm so happy for you both.

45:06.921 --> 45:09.010
Congratulations, Tiberius.

45:09.010 --> 45:12.013
So sorry for you both.

45:14.581 --> 45:16.104
Stepfather.

45:16.104 --> 45:17.540
We came to say goodbye.

45:17.540 --> 45:19.281
Ah.

45:21.370 --> 45:23.590
Antonina.

45:23.590 --> 45:26.854
Goodbye, Antonina.

45:26.854 --> 45:28.595
We'll be
back for the wedding.

45:28.595 --> 45:30.336
Bring me Germany.

45:35.080 --> 45:37.604
I wouldn't mind if it were you.

45:37.604 --> 45:39.388
Be careful.

45:39.388 --> 45:40.955
Someone else
lives inside Tiberius,

45:40.955 --> 45:42.957
and you don't want to meet him.

45:45.438 --> 45:48.484
I'm so sorry

45:48.484 --> 45:51.879
for your father, Tiberius,
and the divorce.

45:51.879 --> 45:56.405
Yes. I'll be married again
in no time.

45:56.405 --> 45:58.973
I'll let you know who it is
when I find out.

46:11.377 --> 46:14.380
Thank you
for bringing him back.

46:17.296 --> 46:20.081
If you want us to wait, we will.

46:20.081 --> 46:22.823
I'll keep my army
in Germany for now.

46:27.480 --> 46:30.396
I love you, Mother.

46:51.591 --> 46:53.811
Don't go back to Germany.

46:53.811 --> 46:57.989
Please, it's not safe.

46:57.989 --> 46:59.164
That's why
he's keeping you there.

46:59.164 --> 47:01.383
No, he isn't.

47:01.383 --> 47:03.472
You're worrying
about nothing again.

47:03.472 --> 47:05.431
I can't lose you, too.

47:13.004 --> 47:15.528
We need to talk about something.

47:15.528 --> 47:20.315
I'll write.

47:20.315 --> 47:21.882
You never write to anybody.

47:21.882 --> 47:24.842
I'll write to you.

47:54.219 --> 47:56.438
Drusus.

47:56.438 --> 47:59.398
We're ready to move again
when you are.

47:59.398 --> 48:02.009
I need to finish this.

48:02.009 --> 48:04.098
- Fucking code.
- Here.

48:04.098 --> 48:12.106
Let me help.

48:12.106 --> 48:14.456
What's so urgent?

48:14.456 --> 48:16.894
It's just something
I want to get off to Tiberius.

48:16.894 --> 48:19.853
Thank you.

48:19.853 --> 48:22.769
"M"...

48:22.769 --> 48:25.598
One-two.

48:25.598 --> 48:27.426
"O"...

48:27.426 --> 48:31.517
Six-eight.

48:31.517 --> 48:35.869
"T"...

48:35.869 --> 48:38.741
Three-four.

48:38.741 --> 48:43.224
Are you sure this is his code,
and not Mother's?

48:43.224 --> 48:45.096
I'm not a complete idiot.

48:45.096 --> 48:46.532
And it is the latest one?

48:46.532 --> 48:50.318
Uh... fuck.

48:50.318 --> 48:54.801
No, it is the right one.

48:57.282 --> 48:59.414
My brother's hand only.

48:59.414 --> 49:02.287
- And this is for Livia.
- Of course.

49:02.287 --> 49:04.419
Uh, I won't make it
back tonight.

49:04.419 --> 49:07.509
Catch us up when you can.

49:07.509 --> 49:08.989
You--come with me.

49:10.599 --> 49:12.166
Mount up.

49:18.085 --> 49:21.349
<i>Tiberius,
I know you won't agree with me,</i>

49:21.349 --> 49:23.612
<i>and Mother never will.</i>

49:23.612 --> 49:26.964
<i>But now is the time to act.</i>

49:26.964 --> 49:30.141
<i>If I bring my legions to Rome,</i>

49:30.141 --> 49:32.186
<i>and you bring yours
from the Balkans,</i>

49:32.186 --> 49:34.710
<i>Stepfather will have to cede power.</i>

49:34.710 --> 49:38.192
<i>If we act together,
we can restore the Republic</i>

49:38.192 --> 49:40.107
<i>without bloodshed or war.</i>

49:40.107 --> 49:41.630
For Livia,
from Antonina.

49:41.630 --> 49:43.197
<i>But I cannot do it alone.</i>

49:43.197 --> 49:45.721
<i>It will take
both of us together--</i>

49:45.721 --> 49:47.375
<i>an overwhelming show of force.</i>

49:47.375 --> 49:50.074
For Tiberius Nero from Drusus.

49:50.074 --> 49:53.120
<i>Think this over.
Give me your answer.</i>

49:53.120 --> 49:55.514
<i>And don't tell Mother
or Piso.</i>

49:55.514 --> 50:00.519
Impressive,
even by your standards.

50:00.519 --> 50:03.652
Leave us, please.

50:03.652 --> 50:06.873
Antonina, I assume.

50:06.873 --> 50:08.266
Give me the letter.

50:31.245 --> 50:33.943
Write back.

50:33.943 --> 50:35.989
You want me to tell him
I support Stepfather.

50:35.989 --> 50:38.078
What choice do we have?

50:38.078 --> 50:39.514
We could poison Stepfather

50:39.514 --> 50:41.168
and bring out
that will you forged,

50:41.168 --> 50:45.390
naming Drusus as successor.

50:48.088 --> 50:49.568
Or not.

50:53.093 --> 50:54.312
Mother...

50:56.966 --> 51:01.580
...when I was a baby,

51:01.580 --> 51:04.713
did you suffocate me
with your

51:04.713 --> 51:06.715
bare hands until I was dead?

51:14.201 --> 51:17.683
Yes. Why?

51:21.991 --> 51:26.779
Well, I guess that sort of thing
was bound to happen...

51:26.779 --> 51:28.520
sooner or later.

51:32.698 --> 51:34.961
We were on the run.

51:34.961 --> 51:37.355
Bounty hunters found us.

51:37.355 --> 51:41.576
They were all around
in the woods. We were hiding.

51:41.576 --> 51:44.449
And then you started to cry.

51:46.538 --> 51:51.151
- It was me or you.
- I stopped you crying.

51:52.718 --> 51:55.329
When it was safe,
Antigone put you in a stream.

51:55.329 --> 51:57.679
Cold water brought you back.

51:57.679 --> 51:59.942
- I went to the underworld.
- And then you came back.

51:59.942 --> 52:02.293
Someone else came back with me.

52:12.520 --> 52:15.741
I don't believe
in "Bad" Tiberius.

52:18.526 --> 52:21.050
He's just someone Drusus made up
when you were kids.

52:37.328 --> 52:38.894
Now write.

52:40.766 --> 52:43.986
I've betrayed my wife...

52:43.986 --> 52:46.337
and myself.

52:54.345 --> 52:56.390
Now for my brother.

53:11.362 --> 53:13.320
It's an exact copy?

53:13.320 --> 53:16.541
I gave the original letter
to Tiberius.

53:23.243 --> 53:25.419
And the key square?

53:25.419 --> 53:27.508
It's always locked away.

53:27.508 --> 53:30.119
Antonina or his slaves
are always around.

53:36.300 --> 53:40.042
Get it for me.

53:40.042 --> 53:43.916
I can't break the code
without the key.

53:43.916 --> 53:46.223
I-I won't let you down.

54:32.399 --> 54:36.098
Mother said you'd
have to choose between us,

54:36.098 --> 54:38.057
in the end.

54:43.018 --> 54:46.979
Me or Mother.

54:46.979 --> 54:49.286
Mother or me.

54:53.072 --> 54:55.988
She said you'd
always choose her.

55:02.473 --> 55:03.865
She doesn't love you.

55:03.865 --> 55:05.345
<i>She doesn't love you.</i>

55:07.652 --> 55:11.612
- She never has.
- She never has.

55:11.612 --> 55:14.354
- She's a monster.
- She's a monster.

56:04.448 --> 56:05.840
It's you or me,

56:05.840 --> 56:08.190
Mother.

56:10.236 --> 56:12.717
And it isn't me.

56:27.166 --> 56:28.863
Aah!

56:52.496 --> 56:54.454
What have you done?

56:54.454 --> 56:56.543
Come on.

57:12.037 --> 57:16.955
I can't breathe!

57:16.955 --> 57:18.652
I thought I was dead!

57:18.652 --> 57:23.483
I was suffocating!

57:23.483 --> 57:25.572
Oh! It was just a dream.

57:25.572 --> 57:27.661
A nightmare.

57:27.661 --> 57:30.447
It was so real.

57:30.447 --> 57:32.579
Like someone was on top of me.

57:33.841 --> 57:35.669
What are you doing here?

57:35.669 --> 57:39.107
I, I couldn't sleep.

57:39.107 --> 57:42.546
I was in the kitchen.
I heard a noise.

57:46.985 --> 57:48.943
Go back to sleep, yeah.

58:13.228 --> 58:16.667
Domitius, long time
since you were here.

58:16.667 --> 58:18.190
I'm still celebrating
the death of Agrippa.

58:18.190 --> 58:19.670
Won't you join me?

58:22.194 --> 58:24.065
About that...

58:25.545 --> 58:28.722
I just found out.

58:28.722 --> 58:31.551
It wasn't Agrippa
that had your brother killed.

58:33.335 --> 58:36.208
He was set up.

58:36.208 --> 58:40.386
It was Livia.

58:40.386 --> 58:42.475
The wife of Augustus.
